OL,3,CCourt shown footage allegedly showing
OL,4,Cmurder suspect disposing of body parts
OL,6,FA court has been shown footage
OL,7,Fallegedly showing a man accused of
OL,8,Fmurder disposing of his housemate's
OL,9,Fbody parts in a 'bag for life'.
OL,11,FMarcin Majerkiewicz, 42, was arrested
OL,12,Fon 25 April last year, following the
OL,13,Fdiscovery of a human torso at Kersal
OL,14,FDale nature reserve in Salford on 4
OL,15,FApril.
OL,17,FHe denies the murder of Stuart
OL,18,FEverett, 67, who he lived with in
OL,19,FSalford, and is on trial at Manchester
OL,20,FCrown Court.
