OL,3,CCourt shown footage allegedly showing
OL,4,Cmurder suspect disposing of body parts
OL,6,FThe human remains were initially
OL,7,Funidentified but police discovered
OL,8,FCCTV of a man going to the site with a
OL,9,Fheavy bag and returning without it,
OL,10,FManchester Crown Court was told
OL,11,Fyesterday (10 March).
OL,13,FThe footage shows what the prosecution
OL,14,Fallege is one of several journeys made
OL,15,Fby Mr Majerkiewicz to dispose of the
OL,16,Fvictim's body parts.
