OL,3,CCourt shown footage allegedly showing
OL,4,Cmurder suspect disposing of body parts
OL,6,FManchester Crown Court has previously
OL,7,Fbeen told that Mr Everett, also known
OL,8,Fas Roman Ziemacki, was killed before
OL,9,Fhis body was sawn into 27 pieces.
OL,11,FAround 'a third' of his body has been
OL,12,Frecovered from locations across
OL,13,FSalford and north Manchester, jurors
OL,14,Fhave been told.
OL,16,FThe pair lived together in a house on
OL,17,FWorsley Road, Winton, Eccles, with a
OL,18,Fthird man named Michal Polchowski.
