OL,3,CCourt shown footage allegedly showing
OL,4,Cmurder suspect disposing of body parts
OL,6,FProsecutors allege Mr Everett was
OL,7,Fmurdered on the night of 27 March, or
OL,8,Finto the early hours of 28 March, last
OL,9,Fyear. Jurors have heard police
OL,10,Fdiscovered six 'deposition sites'
OL,11,Fwhere human remains were found.
OL,13,FMr Majerkiewicz denies the murder or
OL,14,Fmanslaughter of Mr Everett at their
OL,15,Fhouse in Salford, overnight between 27
OL,16,FMarch and 28 March, last year.
